---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<header>
		<h1>欢迎来到我的网站</h1>
		<p>我是 Ajisai，这里是我记录和分享的地方。</p>
	</header>

	<main>
		<section>
			<h2>关于我</h2>
			<p>这里可以写一段简短的自我介绍，比如你正在学习什么、对什么感兴趣。</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>我的内容</h2>
			<ul class="links">
				<li><a href="/note">📚 课堂笔记</a></li>
				<li><a href="/blog">📝 博客</a></li>
				<li><a href="/artworks">🖼️ 照片</a></li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer>
		<p>&copy; 2026 Ajisai</p>
	</footer>
</Layout>

<style>
	header {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
		color: #222;
	}

	header p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0;
	}

	section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		color: #444;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.links {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.links li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.links a {
		color: #333;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		display: inline-block;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.links a:hover {
		color: #0066cc;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	footer {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
		text-align: center;
		color: #888;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}
</style>